&ograve;ng c&oacute; g&oacute;c nh&igrave;n ra Nh&agrave; H&aacute;t Th&agrave;nh Ph\u1ed1, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb TV Samsung m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh ph\u1eb3ng 49 inch, truy c\u1eadp Wi-Fi mi\u1ec5n ph&iacute;, m&aacute;y pha c&agrave; ph&ecirc; Nespresso ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i v&agrave; b&agrave;n l&agrave;m vi\u1ec7c, sofa tho\u1ea3i m&aacute;i. Ph&ograve;ng t\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l&aacute;t c\u1ea9m th\u1ea1ch ngo\u1ea1i nh\u1eadp sang tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 s\u1eefa t\u1eafm, r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t t\u1eeb d&ograve;ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m cao c\u1ea5p Black c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u Appelles n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng. Ph&ograve;ng c&oacute; \u0111i k&egrave;m v\u1edbi quy\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng khu v\u1ef1c Signature Lounge, v\u1edbi c&aacute;c \u0111\u1eb7c quy\u1ec1n g\u1ed3m: b\u1eefa s&aacute;ng t\u1ef1 ch\u1ecdn, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed3 u\u1ed1ng kh&ocirc;ng c\u1ed3n v&agrave; r\u01b0\u1ee3u vang s\u1ee7i trong ng&agrave;y, v&agrave; s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed3 u\u1ed1ng c&oacute; c\u1ed3n k&egrave;m \u0103n nh\u1eb9 t\u1ef1 ch\u1ecdn v&agrave;o bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-48t081oh fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-6 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-48t081p5 fg-row row     fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-48t081pf fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><h2 class=\"ffb-id-48t081ph fg-heading text-left    fg-text-dark\">QUY\u1ec0N L\u1ee2I &amp; TI\u1ec6N NGHI<\/h2><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-48t081pi fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-6 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-48t081pk fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p>- Ph&ograve;ng kh&ocirc;ng kh&oacute;i thu\u1ed1c<\/p>\n<p>- C&oacute; quy\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Signature Lounge<\/p>\n<p>- C&oacute; \u0111i\u1ec1u h&ograve;a kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute;<\/p>\n<p>- Trang b\u1ecb m&aacute;y pha c&agrave; ph&ecirc; Nespresso<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-48t081pl fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-6 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-48t081p